######################################################################
This file contains all information about the Employee Management System
######################################################################

(Login Users)
- Admin
- Employee
- Trainer 

######################################################################

######################################################################

(Admin Controls)
---------------------

- Holidays
  - Allow Recurring With Holiday Events
  - Delete Holiday Events
  - Can Add Holiday Events 

- About / Contact
  - Can Edit All Information on the page (Located : Bottom Right)

- Employee Management 
  - Can View All Current Employees
  - Can View Each Individual information of a Employee
  - Can Edit Each Individual information of a Employee
  - Can Add a new Employee
  - Can Export Employees Details to a CSV file (Located : Top Right)
  - Can View Training Sessions
  - Can Add Training Sessions to a Employee
  - Can Mark of Trainings
  - Can Export Training Records 

- Departments
  - Can View all Departments
  - Can View all Employees inside each Department
  - Can Delete Any Department
  - Can Add a new Department

- Payroll
  - Can View all Employees Payslips
  - Can Export Payslips 
  - Can Generate new Weekly Payslips
  - Can View Personal Payslip

- Leave Management
  - Can Apply For Leave
  - Can View all Leave Forms
  - Can Approve or Reject Leave Forms
  - Can View all Personal Leave Forms
  
- Grievances Management
  - Can Sumbit new Grievances Forms
  - Can View Personal Grievances Forms
  - Can View All Grievances Forms
  - Can Respond and Close Grievances Forms3
  - Can Export all Grievances Forms

######################################################################

######################################################################

(Employee Controls) 
---------------------

- My Training
  - Can View All Personal Training 
  - Can Export All Personal Training 
- My Pay
  - Can view All Payslips 
  - Note : When clicked on a Payslip it will show all Details
  - Can Export All Payslips
- Holidays
  - Can View all Upcoming Holiday Events
  - Can Allpy For Leave (Which takes you to the Leave Form)
- About / Contact
  - Can View All Information on the Contact Page
- Leave Form
  - Can apply For Leave
  - Can View all Personal Leave Forms

######################################################################

